---
// PersonalInfoCard.astro
---
<div class="metal-card p-6 w-full">
  <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold">Your Name</h1>
  <p class="mt-2">
    Welcome to my digital space. Here I explore topics in web development, design, and technology.
  </p>
</div>

<style>
  .metal-card {
    background-image: url('/blackmetal.jpg');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    position: relative;
    isolation: isolate;
  }

  .metal-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    z-index: -1;
  }

  h1 {
    color: #FFFFFF;
  }
  p {
    color: #CCCCCC;
  }
</style>